Package odu.edu.cs.cs350.pne

Class InitialTrainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • odu.edu.cs.cs350.pne.InitialTrainer
  • public class InitialTrainer
extends java.lang.Object
    The Initial Trainer creates an initial arff file from raw train data (until sample files are provided) if no file already exists. In other words, it creates an arff file on the program's first execution.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors
